"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"What is journalism doing right now for the whole human community? How many content are we producing? Are they useful? Are they meaningful? Do they help citizens to take better decisions? Is journalism at the service of people? Is it advocating for the poorest? Is there any possible approach to avoid the so called 24/7 news cycle to produce less with more impact? Can journalism rebuild common ground of conversation in a polarized society?\\n\\nThe Slow News approach is a possible positive answer to all these questions.\\n\\nI devoted my worklife to this concept and to bring together different people with similar approach to journalism. \",\"timestamp\":1640306808,\"title\":\"The Slow Journalist\"},\"digest\":\"drhBBaLPMJboijIcM4-D3imq36NkrXzanC-uwRDpYS4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xfDD67dbe335416345360626Fb7A74022e37fe96d\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"IvDy4RYFXjztsBYfzXZIeLkuizgibaAROFsIeeuB66w\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NB23leEUUbPT4AnANE2wruAQfgreSYp4Ncv6muDSwBk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"WVZIs9hY8JmBH7Wk_MrWYEgAuvaiuez0fQe6vzCxMtvtWOp3rHezdxF_DIiIywbt07W0uIzPVnFU9aX9dveOfg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x66ef7560822f6ceaafa6fb5fa10f34c06d6212d537c2cfb4f959c309ff2d8fb86162e633c74aa8955d49a56399f3749321fb4d85858e307770ceda23958125881c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"IvDy4RYFXjztsBYfzXZIeLkuizgibaAROFsIeeuB66w\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NB23leEUUbPT4AnANE2wruAQfgreSYp4Ncv6muDSwBk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Z45qul2aUZklJZApPjtf95RK5UUWyq80uY7D-nT5vUI\"}"